snippet.title: Gearshifters - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
#GearShifters #NumskullGames #NumskullPresents
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1017160/
Find out more: http://numskullgames.com/project/gearshifters/

Platforms: Steam, Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S, Xbox Series X
Release Date: September 2021
Petrolhead shooter Gearshifters is a dream combination for shoot-em-up and driving fans. 

The experience is both narrative and action-driven, based on a dystopian future reality. Dodge bullets, perform handbrake turns, and shoot your way to victory.
